User Stories

  This document describes the (initial) set of user stories as well as the
roles users have when using the Smart Reservation System (SRS).

* 1. Roles

  <<Admin:>> The administrator manages Buildings, reservations, equipment, users, etc...

  <<User:>> Can reserve certain rooms. A user can have different rights,
  for example a professor has a bigger pool of possible reservations than a student

  <<Non-registerd User:>> Can view reservations but with limitations. He can register but has to wait for the admins
  approval. He may also view reservation prices.


